---
title: Pork and Apple Burger with Rosemary Potatoes and Mixed Green Salad
description: Pork and apple are a match made in heaven. Made into a juicy burger with a brioche bun, it doesn’t get much better than this. Roasted rosemary potatoes and a leafy side salad are the perfect accompaniment.
